Sec. 147.062. FAILURE TO POST COPY OF BOND. (a) A person
commits an offense if the person fails to post a copy of the person's
bond in accordance with Section 147.027 of this code.
(b) An offense under this section is a misdemeanor punishable
by a fine of not more than $100.
(c) A person commits a separate offense each day that the copy
is not posted.
Statute text rendered on: 8/6/2022

